[{"id":14888,"date":"2024-07-18T15:57:03","modified":"2024-07-18T15:57:06","slug":"aephia-turns-three","link":"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/aephia-turns-three\/","title":{"rendered":"Aephia turns THREE!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>Three years ago, on July 18th, 2021, Prometheus &amp; Funcracker officially opened the doors to one of the first Star Atlas DACs (Decentralized Autonomous Corporations\u2014aka guilds. <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Aephia Industries<\/a>&#8216; vision has<\/span><\/em> <em><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">resonated with well over 2000 Star Atlas enthusia<\/span>sts since then. It\u2019s your support that has brought us to where we are today. Thank you for choosing to build your Star Atlas home with us and for all the support you\u2019ve provided!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>These past few years have been challenging for the Star Atlas community, with many early supporters moving away from Star Atlas and even from crypto (gaming) altogether. However<\/em>,<em> you are still with us, and that is what matters most! The team continues to build, and we remain building right alongside them.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>If you\u2019ve recently joined the community, are still looking for a DAC to join, and are excited by the economic opportunities offered by Star Atlas&#8217; 4X\/Grand Strategy gameplay, we invite you to consider Aephia Industries. We would welcome you with open arms, keeping you up-to-date with the latest news, gameplay, and strategies!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Aephia Industries Trailer 2022\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/_R83OFwfGLw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen src=\"about:blank\" class=\"lazyload\" data-load-mode=\"0\"><\/iframe>\n<\/div><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Our trailer from back in the day, but it&#8217;s still very much on-point!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Congratulations, Aephians!<\/strong> We\u2019re three years into the Star Atlas roller coaster, and we\u2019ve certainly been through a lot together! The brutal bear cycle, the significant delay of the mini-game (SAGE), shifting priorities within the team, and impactful events such as FTX and team downsizing have unfortunately driven many away. We\u2019ve come to regard some of those who left as friends, and we hope they will return once the situation stabilizes and the prospects look brighter. Meanwhile, we are fully aware the project has lost some for good.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Today, the Star Atlas community is a shadow of what it was two years ago. Even now, as SAGE profitability remains elusive for many, we see faith in the project wavering. It\u2019s not always easy to remain steadfast amid the turmoil, both for the team and for ourselves as a dedicated Star Atlas DAC.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Fortunately, there has always been light at the end of the tunnel\u2014even though some may not have seen it or felt the tunnel was simply too long. At Aephia Industries, we maintain a bird\u2019s-eye view of the project and adopt a long-term perspective. Instead of getting caught up in the daily drama, hype, or silence (lack of new things), we have focused on building and progressing, keeping our sights set on where the team is headed, not just where their products stand today. Still, throughout this period, we have consistently kept people informed, engaged, and thriving within this ecosystem\u2014to the fullest extent possible\u2014every single day!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"817\" height=\"817\" src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/logo_3rd_anniv2.png\" alt=\"logo 3rd anniv2\" class=\"wp-image-14890\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/logo_3rd_anniv2.png 817w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/logo_3rd_anniv2-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/logo_3rd_anniv2-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/logo_3rd_anniv2-768x768.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 817px) 100vw, 817px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Aephia Anniversary PFP 2024<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Over the past three years, we have been working hard to align Aephia Industries to our founders&#8217; original vision: <em>to create a Star Atlas-focused, self-governed community of like-minded individuals, offering a gamified layer that envelops Star Atlas, and providing fertile ground for projects that can help push Star Atlas to greater heights<\/em>. Our recent management restructuring and Community Expert refresh are testaments to our commitment\u2014not to maintain the status quo but to continually strive for improvement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">COPA &#8217;24 Winners<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In recognition of that unwavering commitment, the team saw fit to award us <a href=\"https:\/\/hologramnews.com\/aephia-crowned-as-2024-star-atlas-copa-champions\/\"><strong>FIRST place<\/strong><\/a> in the COPA competition earlier this year! The <em>Council of Peace Assembly<\/em> (COPA) is a competition between DACs (guilds), spanning two rounds. Initially, participating DACs submit a pitch deck, from which the team selects a handful of finalists to present their DAC live during the COPA show. The jury, comprised of team members, evaluates these presentations based on various criteria to determine the winner. For the second-ever COPA event, we came out on top!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">While winning is, of course, wonderful, COPA also presents a valuable opportunity to showcase Aephia Industries\u2019 latest achievements and forward-looking plans. It\u2019s an excellent occasion to highlight our ongoing efforts and future initiatives to the community. We highly encourage you to explore our <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/copa-presentations\/\">pitch decks and presentations<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Star Atlas COPA 2024 Winners: Aephia Industries\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/gEKH5JKkwnY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen src=\"about:blank\" class=\"lazyload\" data-load-mode=\"0\"><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Breakpoint &#8217;23 &amp; &#8217;24<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We had a great number of Aephians join the special Community Meetup that took place during Solana&#8217;s Breakpoint in Amsterdam last year (a few of them are shown below). All of them (including a number of team members) went home with a limited edition Aephia-hoody. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-768x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG 4257 1\" class=\"wp-image-14896 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-225x300.jpeg 225w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-1536x2048.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-1320x1760.jpeg 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/IMG_4257-1-scaled.jpeg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/1024;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Breakpoint &#8217;23 Community Meetup \u2013 A few of the Aephians present &amp; Michael Wagner (CEO ATMTA)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We look forward to seeing even more of you this year during the <em>Star Atlas Impact Summit<\/em>, which takes place on the 2nd day of Breakpoint in Singapore. We&#8217;ll make sure to bring limited edition T-shirts and some other fun trinkets to all Aephians attending! <em>Make sure to use the dedicated Discord thread to make your presence known beforehand!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1020\" height=\"684\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/image.png\" alt=\"image\" class=\"wp-image-14901 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/image.png 1020w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/image-300x201.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/image-768x515.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1020px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1020\/684;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Breakpoint &#8217;23 &#8211; Michael Wagner rocking our hoody on the mainstage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Celebration<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">As you&#8217;ve likely grown accustomed to, we prefer to spread the festivities concerning our anniversary over several days or even a full week. Each day, we like to share a bit of our knowledge with the community or have some other kind of fun small release. This year is no exception! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Last year, we <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/aephia-industries-dark-core-roasters-enjoy-a-cup-of-aephian-pulse-drive\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">collaborated<\/a>&nbsp;with our friends at&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/darkcoreroasters.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dark Core Roasters<\/a>, offering a special, limited-edition Aephian brew to the community and giving away some for free. We launched a social campaign on top of Never Alone, dubbed&nbsp;<em>Stronger Together<\/em>, and released (members-only) the LitePaper for our NFT campaign:&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https:\/\/aeplife.io\/\">AEP Life Form<\/a><\/em>!<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"11755\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-683x1024.png\" alt=\"AEPHIAN EXTRACT GROUND COFFEE 12oz 340g\" class=\"wp-image-11755 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-683x1024.png 683w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-200x300.png 200w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-768x1152.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-1024x1536.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-1365x2048.png 1365w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-1320x1980.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g.png 1600w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 683px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 683\/1024;\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"417\" data-id=\"13569\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-1024x417.png\" alt=\"AEP Life Form (ALF) - Unique 1-of-1 art\" class=\"wp-image-13569 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-1024x417.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-300x122.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-768x313.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-1536x626.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-2048x834.png 2048w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/1of1s-1320x538.png 1320w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/417;\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" data-id=\"11843\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Stronger-Together-Banner-1-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Stronger Together\" class=\"wp-image-11843 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Stronger-Together-Banner-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Stronger-Together-Banner-1-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Stronger-Together-Banner-1-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Stronger-Together-Banner-1.png 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/576;\" \/><\/figure>\n<figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">Throwback to last year&#8217;s (2023) celebrations!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This year, we are going back to our roots and our first-anniversary week, which we dubbed <em>Knowledge Sharing Week<\/em>. The focus is entirely on sharing knowledge through various media. This year, we have <em>guides<\/em>, an <em>interview with Michael Wagner<\/em>, and an <em>open session on Starbased Automation<\/em>. In addition, now that ALF is out of the door, we will focus on another major project we&#8217;ve been working on diligently over the past two years: <strong>Cataclysm<\/strong>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Cataclysm: Battle for Iris | Gameplay Teaser\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/TeSExIoueNE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen src=\"about:blank\" class=\"lazyload\" data-load-mode=\"0\"><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We&#8217;re going to keep some things under wraps a little longer, but we&#8217;re providing the current planning for this week-long celebration below!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Note: <em>To right away squash any hype\/hope, the Cataclysm event is best comparable to our LitePaper launch event last year in scope. So, nope, this is not yet the full release!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Anniversary Schedule<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We&#8217;ve got some great things in store, with a key focus on <em>sharing knowledge<\/em>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24-1024x576.jpeg\" alt=\"Aephia Anniversary Schedule 24\" class=\"wp-image-14897 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24-300x169.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24-768x432.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24-1320x743.jpeg 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Aephia-Anniversary-Schedule-24.jpeg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/576;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Aephia Anniversary Schedule 24<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Today, on the day of our anniversary, the team will host an event that is dear to our hearts: the second edition of Developer Hour! In addition, we&#8217;ll publish an intro to Starbased that is an optional starting point for new players to dive into the brand new Starbased manual we are releasing over the next few days!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The days after that will be filled with some cool releases and events, with an interview with Michael (by ME) and a small Cataclysm celebration as stand-out events! Check the full schedule out below!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Thursday \u2013 July 18th<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Developer Hour (16:00 UTC) &#8211; Courtesy of ATMTA<br>Learn how to make use of the composability Star Atlas offers through its on-chain programs. <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Publication of <strong>Starbased Guide &#8211; Part 0<\/strong><br>This is an intro to Star Atlas, SAGE, and Starbased, and a look back at how we came here\u2014a great place to start your Starbased journey or reminisce about the past.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Friday \u2013 July 19th<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Brand new <strong>Interview with Michael Wagner<\/strong> (CEO ATMTA) by the one and only <em>Metaverse Explorer<\/em>! Believe it or not, this is the first time ME gets to interview the big man himself!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Saturday \u2013 July 20th<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>SAGE Starbased Automation 101<\/strong> &#8211; <em>Live<\/em>!<br>Learn how to use automation to make your life a lot easier playing Starbased! Everyone&#8217;s favorite Data Runner, Viktor, will explain it all and answer any questions you might have! This event will be organized in the public section of our Discord server and is <strong>OPEN TO ALL<\/strong>!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sunday \u2013 July 21st<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Publication of <strong>Starbased Guide &#8211; Part 1<\/strong><br>The long-awaited update to the SAGE Guide &#8211; Part 1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Monday \u2013 July 22nd<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Cataclysm: Battle for Iris<\/strong><br>Stay tuned for more details!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tuesday \u2013 July 23rd<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Aephia Content Highlights<\/strong><br>Viktor and Funcracker sit down to discuss everything Aephia has to offer and has offered content-wise<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wednesday \u2013 July 24th<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Publication of <strong>Starbased Guide &#8211; Part 2<\/strong><br>That next chapter of our missing manual, which was so far&#8230; missing.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Congratulations!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">To wrap this up, to all Aephians: Thank you for being here and for putting in your time and effort to make Aephia Industries the wonderful community it is today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We are grateful to all community members who have actively participated within Aephia these last few years! A special shout-out has to go to our <strong>Community Experts<\/strong>, <strong>Metaverse Explorer<\/strong>, our <strong>Data Runners<\/strong>, and our <strong>ALF &amp; Cataclysm teams<\/strong>! You have all contributed in a major way to shaping Aephia into the terrific home among the stars it is today! You have our eternal thanks!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Happy 3rd-anniversary, everyone!<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Aephia Industries celebrates its 3rd anniversary! We\u2019re three years into the Star Atlas roller coaster, and we\u2019ve certainly been through a lot together! To celebrate we&#8217;re sharing our knowledge freely with all of you during a week full of gifts from us to you!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2}]